com.github.alex.zuy.boilerplate.api.annotations

Annotation Type GenerationStyle


  • public @interface GenerationStyle
    Annotation for configuring code generation style(e.g. names).

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      String propertiesClassName
      Properties class name format.
      String relationshipsClassName
      Relationships class name format.
      String relationshipsClassTerminalMethodName
      Relationships class terminal method name format.
      GenerationStyle.StringConstantStyle stringConstantStyle
      String constant fields name style.

    • Element Detail

      • propertiesClassName

        public abstract String propertiesClassName
        Properties class name format.

        Format must contain placeholder value ${beanClassName} which will be substituted with simple name of bean class.

        Returns:
        properties class name format
        Default:
        "${beanClassName}_p"

      • relationshipsClassName

        public abstract String relationshipsClassName
        Relationships class name format.

        Format must contain placeholder value ${beanClassName} which will be substituted with simple name of bean class.

        Returns:
        relationships class name format
        Default:
        "${beanClassName}_r"

      • relationshipsClassTerminalMethodName

        public abstract String relationshipsClassTerminalMethodName
        Relationships class terminal method name format.

        Format must contain placeholder value ${beanPropertyName} which will be substituted with corresponding bean property name.

        Returns:
        relationships class terminal method name format.
        Default:
        "${beanPropertyName}Property"

      • stringConstantStyle

        public abstract GenerationStyle.StringConstantStyle stringConstantStyle
        String constant fields name style.

        Defines style of constant fields names in properties classes. Please refer to documentation of GenerationStyle.StringConstantStyle for available options.

        Returns:
        string constant fields name style.
        Default:
        com.github.alex.zuy.boilerplate.api.annotations.GenerationStyle.StringConstantStyle.UPPERCASE
